= Installing environment: =

It is recommended to create symlinks to the files in the tools folder somewhere in your path.

== Debian / Ubuntu Oneiric ==

To install the whole msp430-gcc suite in Oneiric, issue the following command:

  $ sudo apt-get install msp430-libc msp430mcu binutils-msp430 gcc-msp430 gdb-msp430 mspdebug

